<body background="/CLEAR/imgbgs/guitarbg.jpg">


<h1> 
<img align=left border=2 src="/CLEAR/imbars/Guitar2.JPG">
  "While my guitar gently weeps..."
</h1><p>.<p>
<i>with abject apologies, deference, and due credit to <a href="http://www.best.com/~nieh/guitar/"><br>Master Jason Nieh!</i></a>


<p>
<br>
<p>


<img src="/CLEAR/images/Swash1.GIF"><p>

I'm a gross amateur at the guitar which I picked up -such as I could- in my college days in Pennsylvania.  I was weaned on the Beatles, Bob Dylan, and Peter-Paul-&-Mary.  Later I came to Hawaii and fell in love with Hawaiian music which is so much richer and more beautiful than the usual "hapa-haole" tourist stuff that was all I had ever  heard back in the mainland. <P>
I love and play guitar for the sheer joy it gives me.  I only play in for others when I'm among friends who have had enough to drink that they won't notice my mistakes.<p>


<p>
<h2> <img align=center src="/CLEAR/images/Swash1.GIF"><P>Favourite Guitar Music Tablature</h2><P>


