<H1>COLLECTIVE BARGAINING FAQs</H1>
<img src = "Images/thumb.gif"><P>
</center>
Phone: (808) 956-7145; FAX: (808) 956-2023;<br>
E-Mail: <A HREF = MAILTO:"puette@hawaii.edu">puette@hawaii.edu</A>;<br>
To return to CLEAR's <A HREF = "CLEARHome.HTML">Home Page</A>

<img src = "Images/Swash4.GIF"><p>

<H3>Frequently Asked Questions:</H3>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF = "http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/29/ch7.html">The National Labor Relations Act, 29 U.S.C. Chapter 7</li>
<LI>
<A HREF ="CB-FAQ.html#Q1">What Are the Basic Rights of Employees?</A></li>
