EdCI 563J SEC. 1101 CRN 1170 PICD:BIL/BICULT -- ISSUES IN
MULTICULTURAL EDUCATION - PARENTING IN A MULTICULTURAL SOCIETY (1
cr)</strong><br>
This course is designed to help teachers understand the importance of
the role of parents as educators in a multicultural society.  It will
focus on the factors that affect parent involvement from language
minority families, as well as the school's perspective, and how parent
involvement can be maximized to promote biliteracy and
