EdCI 574I SEC. 1101 CRN 3067 PICD:HUMANITIES -- INTERGENERATIONAL
MAGIC (3 crs)</strong><br>
This course is a continuation and practical application of the
<em>Intergenerational Rainbows </em> course.  It is designed to
provide hands-on opportunities for educators (classroom teachers,
