<TITLE> Research Library </TITLE>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<img src = "Images/hResearchLibrary.GIF"><P>
<img src = "Images/thumb.gif"><P>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<FONT SIZE=2>Phone: (808) 956-7145; FAX: (808) 956-2023;
E-Mail: <A HREF = "MAILTO: puette@hawaii.edu">CLEAR</A>;<br>
