<A HREF ="laws2.html#TDI">Hawai'i Temporary Disability Insurance Law</A></li>
<LI>
<A HREF ="laws2.html#PHC">Hawai'i Prepaid Health Care Act</A></li>
<LI>
<A HREF ="laws2.html#Quest">Med-Quest/Health Quest/SHIP</A></li>
<LI>
<A HREF ="laws3.html#FMLA-HI">Hawai'i's Family Leave Act</A></li>
<LI>
<A HREF ="laws3.html#FMLA">Family and Medical Leave Act</A></li>
