<h2>                          [Preamble to the]</h2>
<h2>                 Good Laboratory Practice Regulations</h2> <p> 
<hr>
<br></center>
AGENCY: Food and Drug Administration <p>

ACTION: Final rule.<p>

<p>

<hr>
